                        <p>Through pure recommendation and continued customer requests, we went on to supply and install kitchens and appliances directly to local customers. Our aim here was to always provide the best possible service and to make sure we always supplied our products at very competitive prices to help our loyal customers. With us now designing, supplying and fitting, we had an even more in-depth knowledge of the kitchen industry.</p>
